# BEFORE running `npx @spanlens/cli init`:
# Leave this file empty — the CLI will create .env.local with SPANLENS_API_KEY
# and patch the OpenAI route automatically.

# AFTER running the CLI, you only need this single secret:
#   SPANLENS_API_KEY=sl_live_xxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# The Spanlens dashboard holds your provider keys (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini)
# encrypted server-side. The dummy app NEVER sees the raw provider keys —
# `SPANLENS_API_KEY` is the only thing it ships with.
